commit.message:
mn10300.md (andsi3, [...]): Make them set_zn.

* config/mn10300/mn10300.md (andsi3, iorsi3, xorsi3,
one_complsi2, bit-clear, bit-set, iorqi3): Make them set_zn.

From-SVN: r71499

+

+	one_complsi2, bit-clear, bit-set, iorqi3): Make them set_zn.
+
